  <brief_title>Oral Tonapofylline (BG9928) in Patients With Heart Failure and Renal Insufficiency</brief_title>
  <acronym>POSEIDON</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel-Group Study to Assess the Safety and Tolerability of Oral Tonapofylline in Patients With Heart Failure and Renal Insufficiency</official_title>
  <sponsors>
